<title type="html"><![CDATA[Do you believe in Chinese Zodiac what animal are you belong to ?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=689&amp;p=717#p717"><![CDATA[
welcom! 2023 1/15<br />Host:Maggie <br />Happy New Year everyone !<br />I felt 2022 went by so quickly. <br />It's been an incredible year for so many different things, but it's also been a deeply saddening year in other areas.<br /> However I am so optimistic and happy, Yes, I feel positive about 2023. a new year has arrived. Are you  ready to make a new plan for the coming year?<br /><br />this is a tradition we're having Chinese new year on lunar calendar. so  it will coming soon. Are you ready to celebrate this special day with your family.<br />tell us your plan for the lunar new year holiday. would you like share with us ?<br /><br />questions part 1:<br /><br />1. Do you make a good plan for the lunar new year holiday ?<br />2. What’s the special food that your family  have made for this poticular occasion ?<br />3. Regarding the red envelope money, Are you given more ? Or received more?<br />4. During Your life, do you have any unforgettable memories in your past time of new year holiday ?<br />5. Do you believe in Chinese Zodiac<br />what animal are you belong to ?<br />十二生肖：the Chinese Zodiac<br />西方有十二星座，而中華文化則是有十二生肖。十二生肖在英文中稱為「the Chinese Zodiac」，由十二種動物代表年份。據說在不同年份出生的人，會保有該年代表動物所具有的特色。<br /><br />鼠 Rat<br />牛 Ox<br />虎 Tiger<br />兔 Rabbit<br />龍 Dragon<br />蛇 Snake<br />馬 Horse<br />羊 Goat<br />猴 Monkey<br />雞 Rooster<br />狗 Dog<br />豬 Pig<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br />Sect.2. <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/jWCbVrjJe3g">https://youtu.be/jWCbVrjJe3g</a><!-- m --><br />Questions :<br />1. Do you follow the jokes while westerners  are telling ?<br />2. Can you offer a joke for us?<br />3. How about slangs,shareing some interesting slangs you  know ?<br />4. What kind of things can make you feel happy and satisfy ?<br />5. Free conversation as you like. <br /><br />Each person prepares two questions for the sub-group discussion. <br />In the group presentation members take turns to ask and answer questions. <br />The speaking time is two minutes.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">dora</a> — Fri Jan 13, 2023 9:58 am</p><hr />
